### Simple manual test file for VS Code REST Client extension or similar

# Base URL variable (replace if needed)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/v1

### Get all requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/requests
Accept: application/json

### Create a request (requires Authorization header token from login)
POST {{baseUrl}}/requests
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_WITH_JWT

{
  "bloodGroup": "A+",
  "unitsNeeded": 2,
  "urgency": "critical",
  "location": { "lat": 12.3456, "lng": 78.9012 },
  "hospitalName": "Central Hospital",
  "contact": "+1 555 111 2222",
  "patientName": "Test Patient",
  "notes": "Requires cross-matched units"
}

### Patch status to fulfilled (as donor or owner)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/requests/REPLACE_ID/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_WITH_JWT

{
  "status": "fulfilled"
}

### SSE stream (open in browser or curl)
# curl example:
# curl -N {{baseUrl}}/requests/stream
